latestIgtvVideos.title: The Joy Of Being (🔈on)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The joy of being is in laughter under a boundless sky
In watching weightless bubbles rise
In holding on to our dreams and trying
The joy of being is in watching stars on a cloudless night
Soaring into our limitless lives
Our own quiet company at sunrise
And planting roots to thrive.

#TheJoyOfBeing captures the essence of unadulterated happiness in just 'being' through Bubbles. They remind us of happy childhood memories and the effervescent feeling of pure joy.
To evoke the playful and refractive nature of bubbles, we've combined randomly arranged silver bubbles with bluish accents. Crafted in 925 Silver and Synthetic Opals, The Joy of Being is live now on heyshaya.com!

🎞Conceptualised and created by @rhea.gupte ⭐
